79
00:04:06,240 --> 00:04:08,400
Is it a 4.6 miles per hour,

80
00:04:09,040 --> 00:04:11,120
b 14.6 miles per hour,

81
00:04:11,680 --> 00:04:14,080
or c 46 miles per hour?

82
00:04:14,080 --> 00:04:17,040
And I said 14.6 miles per hour.

83
00:04:17,120 --> 00:04:19,520
And that's not slow enough, Neil, I'm afraid.

84
00:04:19,760 --> 00:04:22,960
The answer is actually 4.6 miles per hour.

85
00:04:22,960 --> 00:04:27,520
And we pedestrians walk at an average speed of 3.1 miles per hour, apparently.

86
00:04:28,240 --> 00:04:29,360
Uh-oh, good to know.

87
